<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_3473"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3473-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3473">Reward individual for finding wasted money&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/6386-4049">Jon Galt</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">4 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Provide a financial reward system for exposing wasted tax payer money, providing solutions which save money, or collecting taxes which are not paid. For example, offer 20 percent of the money saved to a citizen who can identify and prove corporate or private tax evasion. Or, rewarded with a percent of the money saved by identifying when special interest groups make deals which waste tax payer money. Change the incentive structure.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_3473" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_3473', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2242&topicID=3473')">Comments (1)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3473"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2242">New Strategies and Techniques</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=reward">reward</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=tax">tax</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=waste">waste</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=incentive">incentive</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_3473"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_3471">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_3471">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_3471', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2242&topicID=3471&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 4 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 28</div><div>Votes Against : 8</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_3471'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_3471" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 4 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 28</div><div>Votes Against : 8</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_3471'))">20</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_3471', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2242&topicID=3471&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
